A bucket name is globally unique.
But a particular bucket reside in a region.

Bucket created in region1 and accessed in region2
===================================================
Latency increases.
Data transfer costs
So s3 bucket created in one region is acessible from any region.

Across region s3 access standard method is s3 transfer acceleration
S3 transfer acceleration
==========================
1.Normal data transfer is through public internet
2.S3 transfer acceleration is through amazon global network

S3 bucket acceleration leverages cloudfront edge locations for data transfer.
From edge location the data is routed through amazon global network(optimised path)

When s3 transfer acceleration is used
====================================
1.Cross region data transfer.
2.Large object upload
3.High latency networks.




